OL,3,CTeen accused of wounding with intent
OL,4,Cto murder appears in Isle of Man court
OL,6,FThis included possession of a knife at
OL,7,FCornaa beach on 6 October 2025,
OL,8,Falongside taking a vehicle without
OL,9,Fconsent, burglary and theft from a
OL,10,Fproperty, and stealing from a vehicle
OL,11,Fthe day before.
OL,13,FThe teenager was remanded in custody
OL,14,Fat the Isle of Man prison, and will
OL,15,Fappear for committal proceedings on
OL,16,FTuesday 14 April.
